\nw[Kuno]Wait, this is different from what I thought! It's
not Saria's husband, it's Sana's husband, right!?

\nw[Kai]Ah, you're here. It's because Tail has a fetish
for cuckolding.

\nw[Kuno]Hey, why are you doing something naughty instead
of focusing on the task at hand!?

\nw[Kai]It's for gathering materials, you know? Didn't you
hear?

\nw[Saria]Um, we generate magical power through sexual
activity and collect that power in a special way.
\nw[Saria]It should have been written in the request...

\nw[Nonna]......Maybe Prae intentionally hid it. She does
have a mischievous side...

\nw[Kuno]...That seems highly possible. Louis doesn't seem
like the type to do something like that...

\nw[Saria]Um, this ruins originally overflow with the power
of succubi... Currently, since there is no core,
magic power does not leak outside, but the
succubus magic power still accumulates inside.

\nw[Saria]So, if we engage in sexual activity here, the
amount of magical power generated will increase.
That's why we're supposed to have sex here.

\nw[Saria]What will you do? It seems there was a
communication error, so if you don't want to,
please feel free to decline.

\nw[Nonna]No, it's not a mistake on your part. And
besides...

\nw[Kuno]Well, it was a sudden thing, so I was surprised,
but if it's just about having sexual activity,
there's no reason for me to refuse.

\nw[Kuno]If more magical power is generated than usual,
then the pleasure will also become stronger.
